Perl-ScriptRunner version 0.01
==============================

Perl::ScriptRunner allows execution of perl script utilizing "fork" and
"do". It prevents loading of another perl interpreter and provides convenient
way to retrieve return code, standard output, and standard error of executed
script.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

